message.content: {"description":"Get recent WETH transfers with optional address filtering and pagination support","endpoint_path":"/api/weth/transfers","method":"GET","path_params":[],"query_params":[{"default":"null","name":"address","type":"Option<String>"},{"default":50,"name":"limit","type":"u32"}],"response_schema":{"fields":[{"description":"Block number where the transfer occurred","name":"block_number","type":"i64"},{"description":"Unix timestamp of the block","name":"block_timestamp","type":"i64"},{"description":"Transaction hash of the transfer","name":"transaction_hash","type":"String"},{"description":"Log index within the block","name":"log_index","type":"i32"},{"description":"Source address of the transfer","name":"src","type":"String"},{"description":"Destination address of the transfer","name":"dst","type":"String"},{"description":"Amount of WETH transferred","name":"wad","type":"String"}],"name":"WethTransferResponse"},"sql_query":"SELECT block_number, block_timestamp, transaction_hash, log_index, src, dst, wad FROM weth_transfers WHERE ($1::VARCHAR IS NULL OR src = $1 OR dst = $1) ORDER BY block_timestamp DESC LIMIT $2","tables_referenced":["weth_transfers"]}
